### SaviorED API Test Collection
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tool

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Test User"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Current User
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get User Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update User Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Name",
  "avatar": "https://example.com/avatar.jpg"
}

### Create Focus Session
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/focus-sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "durationMinutes": 25
}

### Get Focus Sessions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/focus-sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Focus Session
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/focus-sessions/SESSION_ID/update
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "totalSeconds": 1500,
  "isPaused": false,
  "isRunning": true
}

### Complete Focus Session
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/focus-sessions/SESSION_ID/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "totalSeconds": 1500
}

### Get My Castle
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/castles/my-castle
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Level Up Castle
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/castles/level-up
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Global Leaderboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/leaderboard/global
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get School Leaderboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/leaderboard/school
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get My Treasure Chest
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/treasure-chests/my-chest
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Treasure Chest Progress
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/treasure-chests/update-progress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
